Please follow the instructions in the notice. If you have any questions, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Card Was Delivered To Me By The Post Office
body: On April 17, 2021, the Post Office delivered your new card for Receipt Number YSC2190088998, to the address that you gave us. The tracking number assigned is 9205590153708405461725. You can use your tracking number at www.USPS.com in the Quick Tools Tracking section. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
